      "Text": "Funding for this Amendment #7 is provided by the United State of Health and Human Services through the Social Services Block Grant (SSBG), 42 U.S.C. 1397 et seq., CFDA #93.667; 2021, Grant Award #23021NOSSOR (\"Award\"), administered by DCS, with funds appropriated by the Indiana General Assembly, pursuant to the Indiana Code, including Ind. Code §§ 31-25-2-7 & 31-25-2-8(4).",
